{"mode":"editor","version":1,"windowDimensions":{"x":254,"y":23,"width":1024,"height":752,"maximized":false},"grammars":{"deserializer":"GrammarRegistry","grammarOverridesByPath":{}},"project":{"paths":["/Users/joegesualdo/code/node/subtitle-downloader/file"],"buffers":[{"text":"{25}{175}Advertise your product or brand here|contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today\r\n{2944}{3073}Stasis interrupted.|Fire in cryogenic compartment.\r\n{3076}{3183}Repeat.|Fire in cryogenic compartment.\r\n{3186}{3255}All personnel report to...\r\n{3258}{3339}emergency escape vehicle launchpad.\r\n{3342}{3439}Deep space flight will commence...\r\n{3442}{3544}in \"T\" minus 20 seconds.\r\n{9223}{9298}An E.E.V.'s come down.\r\n{9301}{9350}Get down to the beach.|There may be others.\r\n{9353}{9407}Now!\r\n{9743}{9801}Talk to me.\r\n{13670}{13748}All right, all right.|Let's get it going.\r\n{13751}{13834}Keep it together.|Come on. Right.\r\n{13837}{13902}Right. Here we go, Mr. Dillon.\r\n{14065}{14153}Give us strength,|O Lord, to endure.\r\n{14156}{14267}We recognize that we are poor sinners|in the hands of an angry God.\r\n{14290}{14343}Let the circle be unbroken...\r\n{14346}{14405}until the day.\r\n{14512}{14573}- Amen.|- Amen.\r\n{14699}{14779}Thank you, gentlemen.|This is rumor control.\r\n{14782}{14817}Here are the facts.\r\n{14820}{14861}As some of you know...\r\n{14906}{14987}a 337 model E.E.V...\r\n{14990}{15065}crash-landed here at 0600...\r\n{15068}{15130}on the morning watch.\r\n{15133}{15192}There was one survivor...\r\n{15195}{15299}two dead and a droid that was|hopelessly smashed beyond repair.\r\n{15302}{15374}The survivor is a woman.\r\n{15424}{15516}I just want to say that I have taken|a vow of celibacy.\r\n{15519}{15572}- So have we all.|- That also includes women.\r\n{15575}{15625}- Yes.|- We've all taken the vow!\r\n{15628}{15691}- Shut your gob, Morse.|- I'd like to say, that I for one...\r\n{15694}{15752}do not appreciate company policy|allowing her to freely...\r\n{15755}{15806}intermingle with inmates|and the rest of the staff.\r\n{15809}{15920}What brother means to say is we view|the presence of any outsider...\r\n{15923}{16032}especially a woman,|as a violation of the harmony...\r\n{16035}{16080}a potential break|in the spiritual unity.\r\n{16083}{16145}We are well aware|of your feelings in this matter.\r\n{16148}{16259}You will be pleased to know|that I have requested a rescue team.\r\n{16262}{16324}Hopefully, they will be here|inside of a week...\r\n{16327}{16423}and evacuate her A.S.A.P.\r\n{16426}{16471}Don't give us that!\r\n{16474}{16518}What's her medical status?\r\n{16521}{16566}She doesn't seem|too badly damaged.\r\n{16569}{16660}She's unconscious. Can't give you a more|specific diagnosis at the moment.\r\n{16663}{16729}- Will she live?|- I would think so.\r\n{16764}{16809}Look. It's in|everybody's interest...\r\n{16812}{16901}the woman doesn't come out of the infirmary|until the rescue team arrives.\r\n{16904}{16967}And certainly not without|an escort, right?\r\n{16970}{17031}Sir.\r\n{17034}{17136}Gentlemen, we should all stick|to our set routine...\r\n{17139}{17190}and not get unduly agitated.\r\n{17193}{17228}- Right.|- Correct?\r\n{17231}{17333}All right.|Thank you, gentlemen.\r\n{17453}{17523}- All right.|- Better get here sooner.\r\n{17526}{17602}- There ain't gonna be much left.|- Everybody's dead.\r\n{18476}{18525}What's that?\r\n{18528}{18624}It's just a little cocktail of my own mix.|Sort of eye-opener.\r\n{18627}{18684}You the doctor?\r\n{18687}{18771}My name is Clemens.|I'm the chief medical officer here.\r\n{18774}{18846}- Here?|- Fury 161.\r\n{18849}{18929}It's one of Weyland-Yutani's|backwater work prisons...\r\n{18932}{18977}it grieves me to say.\r\n{18980}{19035}Do you mind?\r\n{19087}{19163}This is basically a stabilizer.\r\n{19166}{19235}I really ought to shave your head.\r\n{19238}{19296}We have a big problem with lice here.\r\n{19299}{19359}And when you're feeling better,|I'll give you some clippers...\r\n{19362}{19467}- and you can tend to your private|parts yourself. - How'd I get here?\r\n{19495}{19580}You crash-landed in an E.E.V.\r\n{19583}{19666}Evidently separated from your mother ship|before you hit our atmosphere.\r\n{19669}{19748}You have any idea|how long you were in hypersleep?\r\n{19751}{19799}Coming out the way you did|can be a jolt on your system.\r\n{19802}{19850}Yeah, I'll be sick|for a couple weeks.\r\n{19853}{19921}Indeed.\r\n{19924}{19991}Where are the others?\r\n{19994}{20039}They didn't make it.\r\n{20042}{20125}- What?|- They didn't survive.\r\n{20206}{20261}I have to get to the ship.\r\n{20264}{20337}- I have to get to the ship.|- You're in no condition for that.\r\n{20340}{20432}You wanna get me some clothes,|or should I just go like this?\r\n{20435}{20560}Given the nature of our indigenous|population, I would suggest clothes.\r\n{20594}{20680}None of them have seen a woman in years.\r\n{20733}{20798}Neither have I for that matter.\r\n{20843}{20925}This used to be|a 5000 convict facility...\r\n{20928}{21024}but it's been reduced|to a custodial staff of 25.\r\n{21027}{21083}- Why?|- Keep the pilot light on.\r\n{21086}{21142}The pilot light for what?\r\n{21145}{21224}Blocked furnace.|Natural methane.\r\n{21227}{21314}We have a foundry,|Lieutenant Ripley.\r\n{21317}{21396}The inmates forge lead sheets|for toxic waste containers.\r\n{21399}{21464}How do you know my name?\r\n{21467}{21544}It's stenciled|on the back of your shorts.\r\n{21740}{21821}Release the cable!\r\n{22221}{22281}- Where are the bodies?|- We have a morgue.\r\n{22284}{22389}We put them there until the investigative|team arrives in about a week, I think.\r\n{22443}{22530}- There was a droid.|- Disconnected.\r\n{22533}{22592}There were bits and pieces|of him all over the place.\r\n{22595}{22644}We put what was left|on the rubbish tow.\r\n{22647}{22727}The corporal was impaled|by that safety support.\r\n{22730}{22776}He never knew what hit him.\r\n{22779}{22835}And the girl?\r\n{22838}{22917}She drowned in her cryo-tube.\r\n{22920}{23025}I don't think she was conscious|when it happened.\r\n{23028}{23113}I'm... sorry.\r\n{23575}{23621}What's the matter?\r\n{23624}{23705}- Where is she?|- In the morgue.\r\n{23708}{23763}I have to see her.\r\n{23768}{23815}I have to see what's left of her.\r\n{23963}{24050}Is there any particular reason that|you're so insistent?\r\n{24053}{24151}Yes. I have to be sure how she died.\r\n{24154}{24227}I hate to be repetitious about such|a sensitive subject...\r\n{24230}{24338}but it is perfectly clear|that she drowned.\r\n{24432}{24489}Was she your daughter?\r\n{24536}{24618}No. She wasn't.\r\n{25615}{25672}Could I have a moment|alone, please?\r\n{25675}{25732}Yes, of course.\r\n{26519}{26576}Forgive me.\r\n{27143}{27218}What's she doing?\r\n{27498}{27556}Okay?\r\n{27559}{27621}No.\r\n{27639}{27684}We have to do an autopsy.\r\n{27687}{27727}- What?|- I told you...\r\n{27730}{27793}we have to make sure|how she died.\r\n{27817}{27896}And I told you, she drowned.\r\n{27899}{28030}I'm not so sure.|I have to see inside ofher.\r\n{28033}{28091}You're disorientated.|Half your system's still in...\r\n{28094}{28141}I have a very,|very good reason.\r\n{28144}{28203}Well, perhaps you'd like to|share that reason.\r\n{28272}{28340}Possible contagion.\r\n{28343}{28410}What kind exactly?\r\n{28413}{28471}- Cholera.|- Cholera?\r\n{28554}{28630}There hasn't been a case|of cholera reported for 200 years.\r\n{28779}{28837}Please.\r\n{29702}{29773}Everything's in place.\r\n{29776}{29856}There's no sign of infection.\r\n{29859}{29923}- No indication of disease.|- The chest.\r\n{29926}{29982}Open the chest.\r\n{30173}{30233}Careful.\r\n{30977}{31041}Lungs.\r\n{31083}{31147}Flooded with fluid.\r\n{31181}{31245}Ergo, she drowned.\r\n{31375}{31498}Now, since I'm not|a complete idiot...\r\n{31501}{31602}would you like to tell me|what we're really looking for?\r\n{31807}{31862}Mr. Clemens.\r\n{31865}{31920}Superintendent.\r\n{31951}{32032}I don't believe you've met|Lieutenant Ripley.\r\n{32035}{32082}What's going on, Mr. Clemens?\r\n{32085}{32145}That's right, sir.|What's going on, Mr. Clemens?\r\n{32170}{32216}Well, first...\r\n{32219}{32335}the lieutenant is feeling much better,|I'm happy to say.\r\n{32338}{32396}Second, in the interest|of public health...\r\n{32399}{32462}- I am performing an autopsy.|- Without my authority.\r\n{32465}{32523}Well, there didn't|seem to be time.\r\n{32526}{32571}But it's turned out all right.\r\n{32574}{32631}- There's no sign of contagion in the body.|- Good.\r\n{32634}{32723}But it might be helpful if Lt. Ripley didn't|parade around in front of the prisoners...\r\n{32726}{32776}as I am told she did in the last hour.\r\n{32779}{32824}It might also be helpful...\r\n{32827}{32898}if you kept me informed as to|any change in her physical status.\r\n{32901}{32958}Or would that be asking too much?\r\n{32961}{33056}- We have to cremate the bodies.|- Nonsense. We'll keep their bodies on ice...\r\n{33059}{33131}- till the rescue team arrives.|- On ice.\r\n{33134}{33196}There is the public health issue.\r\n{33199}{33328}The lieutenant feels that there is still|a possibility of a communicable infection.\r\n{33369}{33423}I thought you said|there was no sign of disease.\r\n{33426}{33476}It would appear|that the child drowned.\r\n{33479}{33538}But without the benefit|of proper laboratory tests...\r\n{33541}{33586}it's impossible|to be absolutely certain.\r\n{33589}{33642}I would consider it unwise...\r\n{33645}{33735}to tolerate even the possibility|of an unwelcomed virus.\r\n{33738}{33845}An outbreak of cholera|would look extremely bad on a report.\r\n{33848}{33912}Would it not, sir?\r\n{33935}{34000}We've 25 prisoners in this facility.\r\n{34003}{34052}All double \"Y\" chromos.\r\n{34055}{34155}All thieves, rapists,|murderers, child molesters. All scum.\r\n{34158}{34271}Just because they've taken on religion,|doesn't make them any less dangerous.\r\n{34274}{34331}I try not to offend their convictions.\r\n{34334}{34403}I don't want to upset the order.\r\n{34422}{34479}I don't want ripples in the water.\r\n{34482}{34601}And I don't want a woman walking around|giving them ideas.\r\n{34604}{34709}I see. For my own personal safety.\r\n{34728}{34774}Exactly.\r\n{34777}{34897}I will leave the details of|the cremation to you, Mr. Clemens.\r\n{34945}{35042}They may use the furnace, but I want|everyone back in lockup by 2200 hours.\r\n{35045}{35104}Recorded, sir.\r\n{35721}{35801}- Christmas has come early, Murph.|- What do you mean?\r\n{35804}{35899}- Any dead ox is a good ox.|- You're bloody right.\r\n{35902}{35955}Smelly bastard's all covered in lice.\r\n{35958}{36053}There's only seven of the friggin' things|left, and then we're done with them.\r\n{36056}{36110}God, I hates hosin'|these bastards down.\r\n{36113}{36172}I always get shite|all over me boots.\r\n{36175}{36249}- Sure we're gonna hose these|things down, Frank? - Yeah.\r\n{36252}{36313}If you had the chance,|what would you say to her?\r\n{36316}{36369}- What do you mean, if I got the chance?|- You know.\r\n{36372}{36438}- If you got the chance.|- You mean, casual like?\r\n{36441}{36542}Yeah. I mean, how would you put it to her if you|bumped into her in the mess hall or somewhere?\r\n{36545}{36617}No problem!\r\n{36620}{36689}I've never had any problem|with the ladies.\r\n{36692}{36761}I'd say to her, \"Good day,|my dear. How's it goin'?\r\n{36764}{36826}Anything I could do to be of service?\"\r\n{36829}{36899}Then I'd give her the look,|you know... up and down.\r\n{36902}{36982}And I'd give her the wink,|the dirty smile.\r\n{36985}{37043}- She'd soon get the picture.|- Yeah, right.\r\n{37046}{37133}And then she'd say, \"Kiss my ass,|you horny old fucker!\"\r\n{37136}{37199}I'd be happy to kiss her ass.\r\n{37202}{37273}I'd be happy to kiss her|anywhere she wants.\r\n{37276}{37390}- Yeah, but treat 'em mean, keep 'em keen.|Right, Frank? - Told you before, Murph.\r\n{37393}{37482}Treat a queen like a whore|and a whore like a queen.\r\n{37485}{37552}You can't go wrong.\r\n{37555}{37642}What do you think killed Babe?\r\n{37645}{37707}Beats me. She just keeled over.\r\n{37710}{37794}- How old was she?|- The charts say 11.\r\n{37797}{37894}In her prime. Never mind.\r\n{37897}{37997}- We'll chop her up later and throw her|in the stew. - Right.\r\n{38040}{38097}Hey, Frank.\r\n{38112}{38184}What's this?\r\n{39650}{39719}\"We commit this child...\r\n{39722}{39816}\"and this man|to your keeping, O Lord.\r\n{39832}{39885}\"Their bodies...\r\n{39888}{40017}\"have been taken|from the shadow of our nights.\r\n{40047}{40141}\"They have been released...\r\n{40144}{40252}\"from all darkness and pain.\r\n{40340}{40417}\"The child and the man...\r\n{40420}{40529}\"have gone beyond our world.\r\n{40532}{40623}\"They are forever eternal...\r\n{40626}{40688}\"and everlasting.\r\n{40852}{40992}Ashes to ashes, dust to dust.\"\r\n{41032}{41098}Why?\r\n{41101}{41174}Why are the innocent punished?\r\n{41298}{41379}Why the sacrifice?\r\n{41434}{41484}Why the pain?\r\n{41543}{41620}There aren't any promises.\r\n{41642}{41711}Nothing's certain.\r\n{41714}{41836}Only that some get called,|some get saved.\r\n{41839}{41953}She won't ever know|the hardship and grief...\r\n{41956}{42018}for those of us left behind.\r\n{42021}{42108}We commit these bodies|to the void...\r\n{42111}{42179}with a glad heart.\r\n{42410}{42479}For within each seed...\r\n{42482}{42550}there is a promise of a flower.\r\n{42634}{42685}And within each death...\r\n{42688}{42789}no matter how small...\r\n{42792}{42855}there's always a new life.\r\n{42942}{43016}A new beginning.\r\n{43091}{43207}Amen.\r\n{43210}{43280}Amen.\r\n{43967}{44034}I'll tell you,|it's fucking weird.\r\n{44037}{44100}The only one to survive|that crash is a woman.\r\n{44103}{44153}What trouble can she become?\r\n{44156}{44212}She's already changed everything.\r\n{44423}{44499}What the fuck are we supposed to...\r\n{44602}{44681}I mean it.\r\n{45546}{45620}Okay.\r\n{45623}{45741}There's a lot of talk going around that|we've got some disharmony here?\r\n{45744}{45843}Any you guys want to tell me|what the problem is?\r\n{45914}{45975}Come on.|Speak to me, brothers.\r\n{46007}{46068}All right. I'll tell ya.\r\n{46102}{46166}I don't mind the dark.|I don't mind the bugs.\r\n{46169}{46266}I don't mind wanderin' around in some|cold, wet, damp tunnel for a week at a time.\r\n{46269}{46342}I don't mind anything.|But I mind Golic.\r\n{46364}{46413}That the way you feel about it?\r\n{46416}{46489}Yeah. The guy's crazy|and he smells bad.\r\n{46492}{46610}I ain't going out with him anymore.\r\n{46679}{46771}You got anything to say for yourself?\r\n{46857}{46917}Well, he's going with you.\r\n{46920}{47038}Golic is just another poor, miserable,|suffering son of a bitch just like you and me.\r\n{47041}{47092}- 'Cept he smells worse.|- And he's crazy.\r\n{47095}{47163}Knock off the shit!\r\n{47180}{47252}You got a job to do.\r\n{47255}{47351}I don't want to hear|another word about Golic.\r\n{47387}{47444}Okay?\r\n{47460}{47515}Okay?\r\n{48885}{48967}As I thought, Mr. Aaron.\r\n{48970}{49055}- As I thought.|- You called it, sir.\r\n{49200}{49336}I just wanted to say thanks for|what you said at the funeral.\r\n{49372}{49416}My friends would have|appreciated it.\r\n{49419}{49485}Yeah, well, you don't|wanna know me, lady.\r\n{49488}{49560}I'm a murderer|and rapist of women.\r\n{49620}{49694}Really?\r\n{49724}{49828}Well, I guess|I must make you nervous.\r\n{50187}{50276}- You have any faith, sister?|- Not much.\r\n{50279}{50394}Well, we've got a lot of faith here.|Enough even for you.\r\n{50397}{50460}I thought women weren't allowed.\r\n{50463}{50508}Well, we've never had any before...\r\n{50511}{50611}but we tolerate anybody.\r\n{50614}{50725}- Even the intolerable.|- Thank you.\r\n{50728}{50838}That's just a statement of principle.|Nothing personal.\r\n{50841}{50921}You see, we've got|a good place to wait here.\r\n{50924}{51020}And until now, no temptation.\r\n{51140}{51222}What are you waiting for?\r\n{51448}{51501}We're waiting for God to return...\r\n{51504}{51605}and raise his servants to redemption.\r\n{51645}{51765}Dillon and the rest|of the alternative people...\r\n{51768}{51877}embraced religion, as it were,|about five years ago.\r\n{51880}{51954}- Tempt you?|- I'm on medication.\r\n{51957}{52014}- Hardly.|- What kind of religion?\r\n{52017}{52147}Some sort of apocalyptic, millenarian,|Christian fundamentalist...\r\n{52150}{52206}- Right.|- Exactly.\r\n{52209}{52275}Point is, when the company wanted|to close the facility down...\r\n{52278}{52366}Dillon and the rest of the converts|wanted to stay.\r\n{52369}{52466}And they were allowed|to remain as custodians...\r\n{52469}{52538}with two minders...\r\n{52541}{52605}and a medical officer.\r\n{52608}{52657}And here we are.\r\n{52660}{52723}How did you get|this wonderful assignment?\r\n{52784}{52849}How do you like|your new haircut?\r\n{52885}{52941}It's okay.\r\n{53342}{53430}Now that I've gone out|on a limb for you with Andrews...\r\n{53433}{53510}damaged my already less-than-perfect|relationship with that good man...\r\n{53513}{53570}and briefed you...\r\n{53573}{53664}on the humdrum history|of Fury 161...\r\n{53667}{53723}can you not tell me what|you were looking for in the girl?\r\n{53726}{53798}You attracted to me?\r\n{53801}{53860}In what way?\r\n{53902}{53960}In that way.\r\n{53994}{54064}Very direct.\r\n{54080}{54145}I've been out here a long time.\r\n{54200}{54257}So have I.\r\n{55629}{55757}Hey, Spike.|Spike? Spikey!\r\n{55873}{55957}Are you down there?|What are you doing?\r\n{57016}{57086}I really appreciate your affections...\r\n{57123}{57204}but I am aware that they...|deflected my question.\r\n{57241}{57322}In the nicest possible way, of course.\r\n{57403}{57464}You're spoiling the mood.\r\n{57479}{57548}I have a job to do.\r\n{57551}{57606}I just want to know why we had to|cremate the bodies.\r\n{57609}{